title: Bug 109350: Output parameter not displaying in data set dialog
description: The output parameter is not being displayed in the data set dialog.

EB: The output parameter should be visible in the data set dialog.
SR:

2. Check the query result is stored in the output parameter as an object
3. Open the data set dialog and verify that the output parameter is displayed
